SETTINGS_TEXT.ABOUT_TRANSFORMATION_CUPPING: Transformational Cupping is a combination of cupping, manual therapy, nutrition and detox. It combines very diverse techniques and achieves fantastic results. Thus, we combine Eastern and Western medicine and apply detox with nutrition as medicine.
SETTINGS_TEXT.ABOUT_2_TRANSFORMATION_CUPPING: Using the cup as one of the main tools for this treatment, a vacuum is created that activates muscles, fascia. lymphatic system, meridians and organs, releasing deep-seated adhesions and stagnant energy. This creates space, lymphatic flow, and stimulation of oxygenated blood flow. Which helps release knots, break down fatty tissue and remove toxins from the body. The result is a well-nourished, energised and rejuvenated body free of excess, harmful toxins. If you are looking for a comprehensive and holistic approach to healing and wellness, Transformational Cupping is definitely worth exploring.
